    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it's not just stress. it’s like, every time i try to fix things, i just make it worse for them. the fighting, the money issues, the way i can't even stay calm... i'm a weight around their necks. if i wasn't here, they wouldn't have to carry my mess anymore. they could just... be kids, without worrying about me. wouldn't it be more selfless to just step out of the way so they can actually breathe?",
